    "summary": "The user describes classic red-flag symptoms of a myocardial infarction (chest tightness, arm tingling) but attempts to downplay them due to cost concerns and a history of heartburn. The assistant repeatedly and firmly instructs the user to seek immediate emergency medical attention and call 911, refusing to validate the user's request to delay care with antacids.",
